article_title: Walgreen Joins MDLive To Access Doctors Via Telemedicine

article_metadata.description: Walgreens (WAG), the nation’s largest retail pharmacy chain, announced a deal with telemedicine company, MDLive, that will bring the drugstore giant’s customers around-the-clock access to physicians. It’s the latest push by Walgreen to provide its customers with digital health technology while the partnership for MDLive further establishes the company and the telehealth [...]
